cholson-in-2023.-CREDIT_Kevork-Djansezian_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Jack-Nicholson-in-2023.-CREDIT_Kevork-Djansezian_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Jack-Nicholson-in-2023.-CREDIT_Kevork-Djansezian_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Jack-Nicholson-in-2023.-CREDIT_Kevork-Djansezian_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Jack-Nicholson-in-2023.-CREDIT_Kevork-Djansezian_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>杰克·尼科尔森的一张新照片出现了，这是近两年来的第一张照片。</p><p>如今，这位演员将自己的公开露面保持在最低限度，最后一次出现是在 2010 年的故事片<em>《你怎么知道》</em>中，这是一部广受批评的浪漫喜剧，由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/reese-witherspoon">瑞茜·威瑟斯彭</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/owen-wilson">欧文·威尔逊</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-rudd">保罗·路德</a>主演。</p><p>不过现在，他的女儿洛林·尼科尔森分享了一张罕见的照片，人们看到了他的身影。</p><p>在照片中，尼科尔森和他的女儿在大概是他的书柜前合影，书柜上放着几张黑白照片和许多好莱坞奖项，包括几项奥斯卡奖。这是下面照片轮播中的第九张幻灯片。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DEWBGDtS_21/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div